- 'Category A' refers to a specific category of materials;
- 'Top materials' are those ranked highest based on their total order value;
- 'Performance' is measured by the total quantity sold and total revenue generated.

- 'Sales channels' refer to the different methods or platforms through which products are sold;
- 'Reaped the greatest harvest' refers to the highest total order value;
- 'Fertile channels' are those sales channels that have generated significant revenue.

sql:
SELECT MAX(order_quantity) 
FROM sales_orders 
WHERE total_order_value > (SELECT AVG(total_order_value) FROM sales_orders);

